Redraw for Soccer Brings Great Loss to Hosts
NHK said they would have to change their broadcasting schedule if a new draw was to made for the soccer tournament , then the matches of Japanese team will not be televised live in their country .
Officials of the organizing committee will hold a meeting on Monday to discuss whether the redraw will take place .
The Thai organizers announced last week that they will be forced to make a new draw due to the withdrawal of Brunei 's team .
